track_notes: Easy trail from the nearby chair lift station nearby Berghaus Hohenbogen. Nice outlook from the chair towards OK.
track_title: Ascent from top station of Hohenbogen chair lift

track_notes:
Coming from Madersdorf you can drive up to the start of this track. In winter this road has signs snow chains mandatory.
From the parking place you can walk over the two GMA summits Farrenruck and Bärenriegel to the summit.
Distance 2.9 km, height gain 187 m, takes me 70 minutes including short stops at scenic places.
track_title: DB7MM Ascent from Diensthütte via Farrenruck

track_notes: It was worth walking further along the perimeter fence to a quiet location away from other tourists. It would be faster using the road the whole way rather than the track.
track_title: Quiet place with picnic table and bench

track_notes: Parking place for hiking close to Hoher Bogen 1, 93485 Rimbach, Germany, (49.24049732586002, 12.908694516548342)
